<div class="mb-6 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-start sm:items-center gap-4 sm:gap-0">
  <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
    이 페이지는 관리자 UI 작업 시 참고할 수 있는 컴포넌트와 레이아웃 예시를 모아둔 화면입니다.
  </p>
  <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 w-full sm:w-auto justify-start sm:justify-end">
    <a href="/docs/design_guide_admin" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center h-[38px] px-4 text-sm font-medium rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-white text-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-50">
      문서 보기 (docs/design_guide_admin.md)
    </a>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="space-y-8">
  <!-- Header Pattern Example -->
  <section class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-100 p-6">
    <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">상단 영역 패턴</h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4">
      대부분의 관리자 페이지는 상단에 간단한 설명과 우측 액션(검색, 버튼 등)을 배치합니다.
    </p>
    <div class="mb-4 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-start sm:items-center gap-4 sm:gap-0 border border-dashed border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-4 bg-gray-50">
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">예시: 회원 정보를 조회하고 검색·관리를 진행합니다.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 w-full sm:w-auto justify-start sm:justify-end">
        <input type="text" placeholder="검색어 입력"
               class="w-full sm:w-52 rounded-md border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2 text-sm focus:border-blue-500 focus:ring-blue-500">
        <button type="button" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center h-[38px] min-w-[90px] px-4 text-sm font-medium rounded-md bg-blue-600 text-white hover:bg-blue-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-blue-500">
          검색
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">이 패턴은 users/list, products/list 등 대부분의 리스트 화면에서 재사용됩니다.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- Table Pattern Example -->
  <section class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-100 p-6">
    <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">테이블 리스트 패턴</h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4">상품, 회원, 주문 등 목록 화면은 공통 테이블 스타일을 사용합니다.</p>
    <div class="bg-white overflow-hidden shadow-sm rounded-lg border border-gray-100">
      <div class="overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="min-w-full divide-y divide-gray-200">
          <thead class="bg-gray-50">
            <tr>
              <th class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">이름</th>
              <th class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">역할</th>
              <th class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">상태</th>
              <th class="px-6 py-3 text-right text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">관리</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="bg-white divide-y divide-gray-200">
            <% const sampleAdmins = [
              { name: '홍길동', role: '최고관리자', active: true },
              { name: '김운영', role: '컨텐츠관리자', active: true },
              { name: '이지원', role: '회원관리자', active: false }
            ]; %>
            <% sampleAdmins.forEach(admin => { %>
              <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50">
                <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap text-sm text-gray-900"><%= admin.name %></td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap text-sm text-gray-500"><%= admin.role %></td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap">
                  <% if (admin.active) { %>
                    <span class="px-2 inline-flex text-xs leading-5 font-semibold rounded-full bg-green-100 text-green-800">활성</span>
                  <% } else { %>
                    <span class="px-2 inline-flex text-xs leading-5 font-semibold rounded-full bg-gray-100 text-gray-800">비활성</span>
                  <% } %>
                </td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap text-right text-sm font-medium">
                  <button type="button" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center h-[33px] px-3 text-xs font-medium rounded-md border border-blue-200 bg-blue-50 text-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-100 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-blue-500">
                    상세
                  </button>
                </td>
              </tr>
            <% }) %>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Form / Settings Pattern Example -->
  <section class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-100 p-6">
    <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">폼 / 설정 패턴</h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4">설정 화면은 카드형 섹션과 공통 인풋 스타일을 사용합니다.</p>
    <div class="bg-white overflow-hidden shadow-sm rounded-lg border border-gray-100">
      <div class="px-6 py-4 bg-white border-b border-gray-200">
        <h5 class="text-base font-bold text-gray-800">예시 설정 섹션</h5>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 bg-white space-y-4">
        <div>
          <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">설정 이름</label>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-2">설정에 대한 간단한 설명을 여기에 작성합니다.</p>
          <input type="text" class="w-full rounded-md border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2 text-sm focus:border-blue-500 focus:ring-blue-500" placeholder="예시 설정 값">
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div>
            <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">숫자 설정</label>
            <input type="number" class="w-full rounded-md border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2 text-sm focus:border-blue-500 focus:ring-blue-500" value="10">
          </div>
          <div>
            <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">옵션</label>
            <select class="w-full rounded-md border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2 text-sm focus:border-blue-500 focus:ring-blue-500">
              <option>옵션 A</option>
              <option>옵션 B</option>
            </select>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">설명</label>
          <textarea rows="3" class="w-full rounded-md border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2 text-sm focus:border-blue-500 focus:ring-blue-500" placeholder="긴 설명을 입력하는 영역입니다."></textarea>
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-end pt-2">
          <button type="button" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center h-[40px] px-5 text-sm font-medium rounded-md bg-blue-600 text-white hover:bg-blue-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-blue-500">
            저장 예시
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Dashboard Cards Pattern Example -->
  <section class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-100 p-6">
    <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">대시보드 카드 패턴</h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4">/admin 대시보드에서 사용하는 요약 카드 스타일입니다.</p>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
      <div class="bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-lg shadow-sm p-4">
        <h5 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-1">회원 수</h5>
        <p class="text-2xl font-bold">1,234</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-green-600 text-white rounded-lg shadow-sm p-4">
        <h5 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-1">총 상품</h5>
        <p class="text-2xl font-bold">567</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-yellow-500 text-white rounded-lg shadow-sm p-4">
        <h5 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-1">새 문의</h5>
        <p class="text-2xl font-bold">12</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-cyan-500 text-white rounded-lg shadow-sm p-4">
        <h5 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-1">오늘 방문</h5>
        <p class="text-2xl font-bold">345</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
